| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1635 — Recovery Inhibition (arcusmedia)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b6df423f-49f1-55d7-8341-3a35f76cf0ab"
